ascatter R6 Class

aScatter.Rd

Create a VR 3D Scatter Plot.

aScatter

Format

An object of class R6ClassGenerator of length 24.

Methods

  • data Add data.

  • build Build graph.

  • get Get graph.

  • browse Browse graph.

  • embed Embed graph.

Examples


data(population)

aScatter$
  new(title = "Random")$
  data(
    population, lon, pop, lat, color, size,
    scale = "2 2 2", valfill="1, 9745.6",
    yLimit = 0.2, rotation = "0 90 0"
  )$
  build()$
  embed()
